headline: Nasdaq Halts Charming Medical Limited
summary: NEW YORK, Nov. 26, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- The Nasdaq Stock Market® (Nasdaq: NDAQ) announced that trading is halted in Charming Medical Limited (Nasdaq: MCTA) for additional information requested from the company. Previously, the Securities and Exchange Commission effected a trading suspension in MCTA from 04:00:00 on November 12, 2025 to 23:59:00 on November 25, 2025.
